make[1]: Verzeichnis »/usr/src/reelbox/testing/packages/ash-busybox« wird betreten
sudo rm -rf tmp .root-copied
if [ ! -d tmp/DEBIAN ] ; then mkdir -p tmp/DEBIAN; fi
sudo install -D control tmp/DEBIAN/control
date +%s > ../lastbuild
test -d tmp || mkdir tmp
sudo cp -dr --preserve=mode,timestamps  ROOT/* tmp
for i in ".svn" "*~" ; do \
		find tmp -name "$i" | sudo xargs -r rm -r ;\
	done
touch .root-copied
makeing ash-busybox.deb
sed -i "s/Version:.*/Version: 0.2-20/" tmp/DEBIAN/control
if grep -q Installed-Size tmp/DEBIAN/control ; then \
		sed -i "s/Installed-Size.*/Installed-Size: 13K/" tmp/DEBIAN/control  ;\
	else \
		sed -i /Architecture.*/a"Installed-Size: 13K" tmp/DEBIAN/control ; fi
echo 20 > .build
echo 0.2 > .lastversion
dpkg -b tmp ash-busybox.deb

sudo cp -dr --preserve=mode,timestamps  ROOT/* tmp
for i in ".svn" "*~" ; do \
		find tmp -name "$i" | sudo xargs -r rm -r ;\
	done
touch .root-copied
sudo install -D conffiles tmp/DEBIAN/conffiles
sudo install -D postinst tmp/DEBIAN/postinst
makeing reelvdr-pi-eepg.deb
sed -i "s/Version:.*/Version: 0.0.5.1-18/" tmp/DEBIAN/control
if grep -q Installed-Size tmp/DEBIAN/control ; then \
		sed -i "s/Installed-Size.*/Installed-Size: 643K/" tmp/DEBIAN/control  ;\
	else \
		sed -i /Architecture.*/a"Installed-Size: 643K" tmp/DEBIAN/control ; fi
echo 18 > .build
echo 0.0.5.1 > .lastversion
dpkg -b tmp reelvdr-pi-eepg.deb

test -d tmp || mkdir tmp
sudo cp -dr --preserve=mode,timestamps  ROOT/* tmp
for i in ".svn" "*~" ; do \
		find tmp -name "$i" | sudo xargs -r rm -r ;\
	done
touch .root-copied
sudo install -D conffiles tmp/DEBIAN/conffiles
sudo install -D postinst tmp/DEBIAN/postinst
makeing reelvdr-pi-reelchannellist.deb
sed -i "s/Version:.*/Version: 0.0.9.5-17/" tmp/DEBIAN/control
if grep -q Installed-Size tmp/DEBIAN/control ; then \
		sed -i "s/Installed-Size.*/Installed-Size: 442K/" tmp/DEBIAN/control  ;\
	else \
		sed -i /Architecture.*/a"Installed-Size: 442K" tmp/DEBIAN/control ; fi
echo 17 > .build
echo 0.0.9.5 > .lastversion
dpkg -b tmp reelvdr-pi-reelchannellist.deb

		find tmp -name "$i" | sudo xargs -r rm -r ;\
	done

makeing reelvdr-external-epg.deb

		sed -i "s/Installed-Size.*/Installed-Size: 253K/" tmp/DEBIAN/control  ;\
	else \
		sed -i /Architecture.*/a"Installed-Size: 253K" tmp/DEBIAN/control ; fi
echo 9 > .build
echo 1.0.4 > .lastversion

test -d tmp || mkdir tmp
sudo cp -dr --preserve=mode,timestamps  ROOT/* tmp
for i in ".svn" "*~" ; do \
		find tmp -name "$i" | sudo xargs -r rm -r ;\
	done
touch .root-copied
makeing reelvdr-pi-games.deb
sed -i "s/Version:.*/Version: 0.6.2.3-17/" tmp/DEBIAN/control
if grep -q Installed-Size tmp/DEBIAN/control ; then \
		sed -i "s/Installed-Size.*/Installed-Size: 336K/" tmp/DEBIAN/control  ;\
	else \
		sed -i /Architecture.*/a"Installed-Size: 336K" tmp/DEBIAN/control ; fi
echo 17 > .build
echo 0.6.2.3 > .lastversion
dpkg -b tmp reelvdr-pi-games.deb

test -d tmp || mkdir tmp
sudo cp -dr --preserve=mode,timestamps  ROOT/* tmp
for i in ".svn" "*~" ; do \
		find tmp -name "$i" | sudo xargs -r rm -r ;\
	done
touch .root-copied
makeing reelvdr-pi-pip.deb
sed -i "s/Version:.*/Version: 0.0.8.19453-12/" tmp/DEBIAN/control
if grep -q Installed-Size tmp/DEBIAN/control ; then \
		sed -i "s/Installed-Size.*/Installed-Size: 364K/" tmp/DEBIAN/control  ;\
	else \
		sed -i /Architecture.*/a"Installed-Size: 364K" tmp/DEBIAN/control ; fi
echo 12 > .build
echo 0.0.8.19453 > .lastversion
dpkg -b tmp reelvdr-pi-pip.deb
